  "title": "Whiskey Flicks Live!",
  "description": "WFL! is an unscripted, booze-infused, deep dive into film. Every performance, Daniel shows Michael a unique series of themed movie clips, and Michael responds with improvised comedy and critique. Michael doesn't know what Daniel's gonna play; Daniel doesn't know what Michael's gonna say, and the audience is along for the ride.",
  "credits": "<strong>Cast</strong>: Created and performed by Michael Niederman and Daniel McCoy<br/>",
  "website": "",
  "plain_language": "At each show, Daniel plays a series of one-time-only, themed movie clips, projected onto. a screen for all to see, and Michael provides a running commentary, completely improvised on the spot. The audience is invited to join the fun by making suggestions, talking to the screen, and sharing whiskey (if desired and of-age) with the performers.",
